    "body": "This idea was heavily discussed and ultimately rejected in #10169, related tickets, and IRC.\n\nEffectively managing your production queue is an important part of playing the game (distinguishing between good and bad players), and automating this reduces gameplay depth as well as introducing UI complexity.\n"
