    "body": "Okay, it seems there are two alternative proposals here.\r\n\r\nThe **\"I want it next\"** proposal:\r\n```\r\nBefore: A 50%   B 0%   C 0%              After: A 50%   X 0%   B 0%   C 0%\r\n              ▲\r\n              X\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe **\"I want it now\"** proposal:\r\n```\r\nBefore: A 50%   B 0%   C 0%              After: X 0%   A 0%   B 0%   C 0%\r\n       ▲\r\n       X\r\n```"
